      "text": "How to use: (1) Select a Patient preset from the Patient ▾ dropdown. (2) Click ↺ Re-init. (3) The patient snapshot and HbA1c Risk Tier fill automatically. (4) Insulin Management OR Oral Medications section appears based on the patient profile. (5) Complete all required sections to reach PASS.",
